Command to build the docker after you install NVIDIA-DOCKER:

			nvidia-docker run -ti bvlc/caffe:gpu caffe --version

Used a Docker to run the Caffe Training on Server and Imagenet folder mounted in to Docker using Below Command

			docker run -v /home/LAB/rchamart/Downloads/ILSVRC2012/:/opt/caffe/data/imagenet/ -ti bvlc/caffe:gpu bash

Command to Run it regularly :

			docker run -ti bvlc/caffe:cpu bash


Guide for Dockers:

			https://docs.docker.com/v1.10/engine/userguide/containers/dockerizing/
